Upload a TraveNetz export file for OBIS 1-0:1.8.0 (grid draw, hourly) to import it 1:1 - no scaling, no other entity. Leave both fields empty to skip this step entirely.

"Value at start" is the meter reading at the very first row of the file (0 if it starts at meter installation).

